  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917340/extras/b319273e6214db0b24135feaffda8695.avif?t=1774247588\" width=342 height=228 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>MASTER THE FLUX</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Match gems to level up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Activate powerful abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Story Mode</strong> – Hoka! Into chaos, come.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Hi-Score Mode </strong>– Global leaderboard ranking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>PVP Mode</strong> – Who's more cerebral?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Try The DEMO</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917340/extras/b931e3dba7c3ea4c561311c12d5b079a.avif?t=1774247588\" width=100 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>TIKO</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Under chaos is a precise system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917340/extras/079912753715930632c3ccab0b3cbfd4.poster.avif?t=1774247588\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917340/extras/0799127537159